你在电影里经常看到它。

133
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:53,280
People have pendants and inside they have a nice picture of someone.
人们有吊坠，里面放着某个人的漂亮照片。

134
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:54,280
That's right.
没错。

135
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:55,280
So that's a locket.
所以那就是小盒坠。

136
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,280
All right.
好的。

137
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,280
Very good.
非常好。

138
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:59,400
I think we've taken a look at a lot of vocab related to jewelry here.
我想我们已经看了很多与珠宝相关的词汇。

139
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:00,520
Why don't we go back?
我们为什么不回去呢？

140
