Well, you can give her a set of pearl earrings or this beautiful heart shaped pendant.
嗯，您可以送她一套珍珠耳环或这个漂亮的心形吊坠。

150
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:39,360
What is her favorite gemstone?
她最喜欢的宝石是什么？

151
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,360
That purple one.
那个紫色的。

152
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,360
I'm sorry.
对不起。

153
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:44,160
I've never bought jewelry for anyone and I'm kind of nervous.
我从没给任何人买过珠宝，有点紧张。

154
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,160
Don't worry.
别担心。

155
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:51,160
We specialize in providing our customers a relaxed, pressure-free shopping environment.
我们专为顾客提供轻松、无压力的购物环境。

156
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:53,640
That stone is an amethyst.
那块石头是紫水晶。

157
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:57,020
We have a range of beautiful amethyst pieces.
我们有一系列漂亮的紫水晶饰品。

158
00:06:57,020 --> 00:06:59,000
Take a look at this bracelet.
看看这个手链。

159
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:04,280
It's 18 karat rose gold studded with amethyst and blue topaz.
它是18K玫瑰金，镶嵌紫水晶和蓝色托帕石。

160
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:06,600
It's a great statement piece.
这是一件很棒的抢眼单品。

161
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,680
Oh, wow.
哦，哇。

162
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:10,200
That's really pretty.
那真的很漂亮。

163
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:11,920
Jess would love that.
杰丝会喜欢的。

164
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:17,060
But I was thinking of something a little more delicate, perhaps a necklace?
但我在想更精致一点的东西，也许是一条项链？

165
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:22,520
We have this beautiful platinum pendant or you could also get her a locket.
我们有这条漂亮的铂金吊坠，或者你也可以给她买个挂坠盒。

166
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:24,680
You could also get her a timepiece.
你也可以给她买一块手表。

167
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:27,600
It's both glamorous and functional.
它既迷人又实用。

168
